node.accessibility_caption: Photo by NIKOLE | TARGET BLOGGER in Jacksonville, Florida with @starbucks, and @target.

node.text: HAPPY FALL, Y’ALL! 🍁🍂🤪 lol JK… (kinda) But really, who grabbed a Pumpkin Cream Cold Brew this morning?! It is my f a v o r i t e Starbucks drink & I’m SO happy it’s here! I always get extra ice (bc Florida) & an extra pump of vanilla syrup… try it! It’s so yummy! 😋

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by NIKOLE | TARGET BLOGGER in Jacksonville, Florida with @targetstyle, @target, and @targetactually. May be an image of indoor and text that says 'SNACK BAR'.

node.text: TELL ME! Does your Target have a Snack Bar?! 😍 SO many of y’all messaged me yesterday saying how much you miss Target slushees/popcorn & how they took out your Targets food court! & while all of mine did too, ONE did remodel & made a self serve snack bar where you can still get your popcorn & slushee fix 🎯😋 Target slushees are DEF a new pregnancy craving for me 🤤

node.text: A day late but our big boy started 1st grade yesterday and had such a great time! 📚✏️ I can’t believe how grown up he looks!! 🥺 Has school started where you live? Let me know ⭐️

node.text: Name a cuter smiler than one that’s missing two front teeth 🙈😍 I’m honestly going to be so sad when Braylon’s front adult teeth come in. 😭 In other news, we switched out his old mattress for a new @simmonssleep memory foam mattress & he loves it SO much! Comfortable, affordable, & conveniently packaged in a box! Target is currently running a 10% off discount on Simmons Memory Foam Mattresses now through August 14th - check out my stories to see how easy it is to unbox & to shop! ⭐️ PS: it’s a little wrinkled since we JUST took it out of the box 🤪 #SimmonsPartner
